=Description=

"This video is a short intro to the idea of starting with a mutual credit or single issuer or group issuer community currency or mutual credit - and using a bonding curve to a reserve in expanding that currency into one that can connect to other CICs. These common reserve between community currencies could be tokens that simple represent agreements between the communities or they could be stable coins against National currencies - or both."


